text: Return of the Texan is a 1952 American western movie. It was directed by Delmer Daves. Actors include Dale Robertson, Joanne Dru, Walter Brennan, Richard Boone, and Tom Tully. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:1952 movies Category:1950s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Delmer Daves
